data.title: Bubble Burst
data.description: Burst your way through space in Bubble Burst! Shoot all bubbles of a kind and fill your burst meter. Play this amazing bubbleshooter now!

data.title: Fun Game Play Mahjong
data.description: Play Classic Mahjong in Fun Game Play Mahjong. Match mahjong stones and clear each of the many levels.

data.title: Heroes of Myths
data.description: Deploy your army, choose your god and fight amongst the Heroes of Myths! Legendary heroes will help you defend against otherworldly foes!

data.title: Jelly Madness 2
data.description: The Jellies are back for a new jellicious match-3 adventure! Take out the Fat, Ninja, Fast and Eating Jellies. Enjoy!

data.title: Jewel Burst
data.description: Embark on a mission and collect jewels from the stars. Match 3 or more identical jewels. Play Jewel Burst now!

data.title: Super Stack
data.description: Stack all shapes in Super Stack. A fun physics based super stacker game. Have some stacking fun!

data.title: Twisted City
data.description: Connect the road in Twisted City! A game inspired by Plumber Game. Rotate pieces and solve many of the challenging puzzles.
